<REFEX REG08-TYPE="pronoun" EMPHATIC="yes" HEAD="rel-pron" CASE="nominative">which itself</REFEX>
</ALT-REFEX>
</REF>
 (Occitan: Ventor in classical norm or Ventour in Mistralian norm) is a mountain in the Provence region of southern France, located some 20 km north-east of Carpentras, Vaucluse. On the north-side, 
<REF ID="773.2" SEMCAT="mountain" SYNCAT="np-subj">
<REFEX REG08-TYPE="common" EMPHATIC="no" HEAD="nominal" CASE="plain">the mountain</REFEX>
<ALT-REFEX>
<REFEX REG08-TYPE="name" EMPHATIC="no" HEAD="nominal" CASE="plain">Mont Ventoux</REFEX>
