</ALT-REFEX>
</REF>
 stands alone to the west of the Luberon range, and just to the east of the Dentelles de Montmirail, 
<REF ID="773.9" SEMCAT="mountain" SYNCAT="subj-det">
<REFEX REG08-TYPE="pronoun" EMPHATIC="no" HEAD="pronoun" CASE="genitive">its</REFEX>
